ter says &quot;we&quot; till the close of verse 6; then in verses </div><div class="t m2c2 x26 h27 ya23 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7-12 he says &quot;the disciples,&quot; and &quot;they;&quot; and from that </div><div class="t m6a0 xb h13 ybe7 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IN THE MOST NEEDY FIELDS </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
